FleetParticipant.name: FleetParticipant
FleetParticipant.description: Represents the relationship between a fleet and a participant, such as an account, a contact, or a user.

EffectiveEndDate.description: The date until when a participant is associated with a fleet.

EffectiveStartDate.description: The date from when a participant is associated with a fleet.

FleetId.description: The fleet associated with the Fleet Participant record.

LastReferencedDate.description: The most recent date on which a user referenced this record.

LastViewedDate.description: The most recent date on which a user viewed this record.

Name.description: The autopopulated name of a Fleet Participant record.

ParticipantId.description: The participant associated with a Fleet, such as an account, a user, or a contact.

ParticipantRole.description: The role of a participant associated with a fleet.

Status.description: Specifies the status of the participant in relation to a fleet.
